Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.96,0:24:55.76,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}那麼平凡 卻那麼特別
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.76,0:24:59.06,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}看 若非這雙眼睛
