Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.06,0:25:08.19,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.19,0:25:13.19,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}縱使我能夠轉世重生
